7 Lyovka: derogative or folksy diminutive of Lyov (Leo).

8 antranou etc.: Russian mispronunciation of Fr. entre nous soit dit, between you and me.

9 filius aqua: “son of water,” bad pun on filum aquae, the middle way, “the thread of the stream.”

10 une petite juive etc.: a very aristocratic little Jewess.

11 ça va: it goes.

